text:
Stomachache after eating… was deceived by the queue. Briyani was cheap at $6, taste pretty average but came with a stomachache.
DO NOT RECOMMEND

I ordered via Grab. You can cheat us because we order via Grab not dining in.

Ordered Mutton chop but came chicken instead. No egg? Portion very little.

Nasi goreng Pattaya with mutton. No mutton at all just rice with the egg.

Fried Bee Hoon is hard not cooked properly. no chicken?

Do business properly la, why are you taking advantage over delivery orders. Delivery charge is already expensive yet you do this?? Horrible

Edit: since  July 24 people keep changing..prata is very poor now...
Like plain color, not crisp, curry diluted..
Decent stall. Lamp curry so-so, prata not crispy. Did not like the idea of pre-prepared the pratas and keep it

Hygiene is really terrible.
Saw the stall holder finished smoking and returned to kneel the dough without washing his hands.
They keep touching the loose sweaty black masks and next touch the prata doughs...so dirty.
You will lost appetite just by observing their hygiene level.

The staff always try to hijack customers from walking towards 2nd Muslim stall.
